{"tid":1472070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬你地支唔支持 香港獨立","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:35:14.000Z","uid":305579,"like":155,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"35394da0e26442a7a863a3ae71be74c86578e7c7","tid":1472070,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"究竟係香港人目光短淺, 定真係覺得香港唔需要獨立? 今日即使成功撒回惡法, 一日仲係中共既管治下, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他日都會有第二條,第三條惡法。</span></span>好多人話香港冇可能獨立, 但唔踏出第一步就緊係咩都冇可能。<br />\n事實上, 水可以買, 軍隊可以買, 乜柒都可以買, 差在係我地香港人開始接受現實未。過多廿幾年去到2047, 甚至再早d, 香港正式=支那, 你既下一代就係支那人。香港人, 你甘心咩?<br />\nps 唔係想騎劫場運動, 只係想各位正視香港未來既發展。<br />\n原諒我係P牌仔, 但我係真心為香港。<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮啦港獨撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c81149b273299f400f8a2ab54700b8337b6e444","tid":1472070,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eser